metadata.name: Nyanko-chan
metadata.description:
"Hi! My name is Nyanko. My birthday is June 5th, and I am a Gemini. My blood type is O. My favorite things are playing video games, and going shopping with my friends! Right now I'm at the beach enjoying some sunshine and - oof!" 
"Has anyone seen my keys???" 
"Hey! This is my introduction...."
